## Self-repair architecture (target)
- Error detection: n8n Error Workflow trigger + scheduled health cron
- Diagnosis: Ollama (VPS 2) via n8n AI Agent node
- Action: n8n API (GET/PUT workflows), Docker restart via SSH, alerts
- Logging: empire_events table in Supabase (already exists, already shown in EmpireAuditTrail)
- Dashboard: Empire page shows realtime events

